lead_paragraph: British soccer teams could find it harder to sign top European players and some players may be forced to leave if the country exits the European Union, one of the leading women in the sport said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Britain Leaving EU Would Hurt Its Football Clubs, Chairwoman Says
headline.main: Britain Leaving EU Would Hurt Its Football Clubs, Chairwoman Says
